1.Computer is a device or machine which performs set of instruction or program.

2.RAM is know as random Access Memory 
it is primary memory 
it is volatile in state
it is measured in mhz
it is connected to cpu through motherboard by the bus

3.Where is data stored in pc?
it is stored in HDD or SDD meant secondary memory

4. keyboard

5. output device which displays or omits the processed input given by user devices like monitor,printer etc

